19 日首班车开始，铁路已恢复了正常运行。 震中附近的居民表示，因为担忧深夜再次发生剧烈摇晃，几乎是整夜未眠。 日本气象厅表示，包括该地区在内的内陆浅源地区过去曾发生过大地震，一周内可能连续发生同等程度的地震，并且也存在发生更大地震的可能性，呼吁当地民众注意。日本长野一夜连震 47 次，当局呼吁警惕更大地震"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2f5f4060e4743ce0e1611f2b54894a10_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1896918501169526467"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIxsilwoD8lLoKEAMaCTExNDU3NzYwMCDl6YzABjAAOEtACHITMTg5NjkxODUwMTE2OTUyNjQ2N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1745206571.839032", "card_id": "Q_1896617540551156962", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个世界级前锋和一个世界级中场，比较而言哪个对球队的价值更高？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在五大联赛、欧冠或者世界杯的背景下看，必须二选一的情况下，哪个对一支球队来说是更为重要的存在？ 排除类似「我队里前锋 / 中场人才济济所以我队更需要中场 / 前锋」的巧合或极端场景，正常情况下，一支联赛 / 欧冠 / 世界杯球队对这两名世界级球员二选一的选择是怎样的呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f6a6e28fe129f53248db6a6294507523_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1896617540551156962"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIxsilwoD8lLoKEAMaCTExNDU2NjI1NiCbuYjABjAAOCVACXITMTg5NjYxNzU0MDU1MTE1Njk2MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1745206571.839556", "card_id": "Q_1892250684868511615", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89